<title>Welcome to the Haskell Free Libary and Opera House - Derby Line, VT — Free Opera House and Library</title><meta name="description" content="Opera House

The pride of Stanstead, Quebec, and Derby Line, Vermont, the Haskell Free Library and Opera House was constructed deliberately astride the boundary line separating Canada from the United States. This remarkable institution has attracted visitors from around the world. The subject of an ongoing fascination on the part of the media, the Haskell has been featured on network news around the world and in publications such as Life Magazine, Canadian Geographic, the New York Times, Ripley’s Believe It or Not, and countless others. " />
<meta name="keywords" content="Haskell, Haskell Library, Haskell Opera House, Quebec, Stanstead, Derby Line, VT, Vermont" />
